Package: openaps-recoveryd
Version: __OPENAPS_VERSION__
Architecture: armv7ahf-vfp-neon
Maintainer: OpenAPS <bdbruin@gmail.com>
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Depends: openaps-base
Description: OpenAPS recoveryd — SSH access plane and recovery surface.
 Installs /home/applications/recoveryd/recoveryd and its /etc/rcS.d/S97 BusyBox
 init script. recoveryd owns root's authorized_keys (the source of truth for SSH
 access) and ensures the dropbear host key, providing an out-of-band recovery
 path and the SSH-key management surface the ecu-web console uses.
